# Push notifications

Registry: **`docs/PUSH_NOTIFICATIONS.md`** — update on every new notify event.

When adding background push:

1. `type` in `supabase/functions/send-push/index.ts` (`PushBody`)
2. Handler: auth, membership/role check, quiet hours, suspended skip
3. `notifyX()` in `src/services/pushDispatchService.ts`
4. Call from service after DB success (fire-and-forget, best-effort)
5. `navigateFromNotificationData()` case in `navigationRef.ts`
6. Deploy: `supabase functions deploy send-push --project-ref casljueycxsqexpkdiuq`
7. Test iOS + Android physical devices (background + killed)

Foreground-only Realtime alerts: `src/hooks/useJoinRequestNotifications.ts`, `useGameLifecycleNotifications.ts` — not a substitute for FCM.
